					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12008249#post-4271689</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12008249/scp-4046#post-4271689</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2019 19:46:34 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>RockTeethMothEyes</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4022320</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm a bit on the fence about this one. While I enjoy the events that play out here slowly getting more grim, I'm having some difficulty figuring out if Wonder World!™'s Wondertainment would allow for this to be made. I do see the sticker that says &quot;proof of concept&quot;, but it doesn't seem like a particularly fun toy. It sends a kid through a possible life, which I understand is a fundamental flaw in the concept, <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">but it strikes me as odd that Wonder World!™ denizens wouldn't pick up on that.</span></p> <p>I answered my own question. Upvote.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
