				<title>aw hell</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12008249/scp-4046#post-4268313</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2019 15:51:20 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Uncle Nicolini</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3487700</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0Uc3ZrmhDN4">Life is short, so love the one ya got cause you might get run over or ya might get shot.</a></p> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1559605110" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3337265&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1559605110" alt="Tufto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3337265)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" >Tufto</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aismallard" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4598089&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1559605110" alt="aismallard" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4598089)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aismallard" >aismallard</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1559605110" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" >DarkStuff</a></span>. This was written as part of the 2019 Draft Swap, and was originally a work by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/macwarren" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3741977&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1559605110" alt="MacWarren" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3741977)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/macwarren" >MacWarren</a></span>. There's very little left of that original draft, but it did feature a computer asking what you wanted to be when you grew up. I was feeling like writing for Wonderful World again, so I took that concept and turned it into a faulty not-quite-finished Wondertainment toy.</p> <p>Also, “Magnus is an OLD stupid vain dummy”.</p> 
				 	]]>
